subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Jelena Jankovic won her third title in three weeks, beating Vera Zvonareva, 6-2, 6-4, in the final of the Kremlin Cup in Moscow. On the men’s side, Igor Kunitsyn upset Marat Safin for his first ATP Tour title. Kunitsyn overcame the seventh-seeded Safin’s 21 aces to win, 7-6 (6), 6-7 (4), 6-3.
